{"tid":1640512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最新燒山開盤: 活動的結果~登登登~","createTime":"2019-10-09T03:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:13:48.000Z","uid":190361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"374c3871aa74dcf3b94ffa440b409c24cd33da93","tid":1640512,"uid":190361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"香港問題的結果和解決辦法 〈蕭若元：理論蕭析〉2019-10-08<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jvpU7EGyk8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjvpU7EGyk8A&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=8dd71242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jvpU7EGyk8A</a><br />\n<br />\n蕭生話，香港活動的結果有三: (0:38)<br />\n1. <strong>「北京妥協」</strong> (完全妥協五大訴求的定案)<br />\n「我所了解的北京，係唔會妥協，會做到底，會強硬」(0:49)<br />\n「雙普選係短期內難以應承」(2:35)<br />\n「獨立調查委員會都難以應承」(2:40)<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>「不了了知」</strong><br />\n「示威者會不會散呢? 我話比你想，係難以會散，亦都係難以會散」(3:33)<br />\n「我唔相信香港人會做到<strong>激烈</strong>到好似北愛咁，即係<strong>用炸彈</strong>去炸死，hou民建聯開大會果時炸Q死哂全部人」(7:42)<br />\n「但係呢?會唔會有幾個人偷偷地襲擊何君堯呢? 我唔排除啦。」(8:01)<br />\n「有一部人係會轉了做了和理非」(8:38)<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>「雙方妥協」</strong><br />\n「冇得settle」(9:35)<br />\n「冇人可以<strong>做代表</strong>同政府講野」(9:42) (仆街, 有大台預言)<br />\n「<strong>我所講嘅野，根本係唔重要，即係我所講嘅野對於前線係完全影響唔到</strong>。」(9:49)<br />\n<br />\nconclusion:<br />\n「我嘅expectation，呢件事係沒完沒了，係以年數拖落去」(11:25)"},{"pid":"6f80d2f7f204456ec1974379f8a2af49c957af67","tid":1640512,"uid":22796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:57:34.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n不如唔好講啦<br />\n喺度燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5014ae2c0181f67d1cde676b0a0b8d6d34f1362f","tid":1640512,"uid":89567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:58:05.000Z","msg":"好心佢唔好登啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0869e138ed83e13541af971e5417383c1ad89278","tid":1640512,"uid":272866,"like":2,"dislik